    <p><b>Indian National</b><br />
        For Domestic Tourists, Inner Line Pass (ILP) Is Required For Entry Into Mizoram For Persons Other Than Government Employees. Inner Line Permit (ILP) Can Be Obtained From The Liaison Officers Posted At Mizoram Houses From These Cities New Delhi, Kolkata, Mumbai, Guwahati, Shillong, Silchar, Vellore And Bangalore. It Can Also Be Obtained On Arrival At Lengpui Airport. 
    </p>

    <p><b>Foreign Nationals & NRI’s</b><br />
        Foreign Nationals No Longer Require Restricted Area Permit (RAP). They Have To Register Themselves At The Office Of Superintendent Of Police (CID / SB) Mizoram Within 24Hrs. Of Arrival. However, Citizens Of Afghanistan, China And Pakistan Require Prior Approval Of The Ministry Of Home Affairs Before Entering The State.
    </p>
